subject: Ice Dancing
Biathlon
lead_paragraph: The reigning ice dance champions Isabelle Delobel and Olivier Schoenfelder of France will miss the world championships, which begin Tuesday in Los Angeles, because Delobel is recovering from shoulder surgery.
